note:
<one animation>

<Post-Damage Eval>
var highestHP = 0;
var person = $gameParty.members()[0];
for (i = 0; i < $gameParty.members().length; i++) {
    var hpCheck = $gameParty.members()[i].hp / $gameParty.members()[i].mhp;
    if (hpCheck > highestHP) {
        highestHP = hpCheck;
        person = $gameParty.members()[i];
    }
}
var newDamage =  200 + user.atk * 1.6 - person.def * 0.8;
newDamage *= 0.25;
newDamage = Math.round(newDamage);
person.gainHp(-newDamage);;
</Post-Damage Eval>
